              <p style={{ margin: "0 0 12px" }}>
                This runs the <strong style={{ color: C.chalk }}>real SensAItion irrigation engine</strong> — every stage
                transition, threshold, alert, and the manual-override logic — either against a simulated field
                or against <strong style={{ color: C.chalk }}>your own sensor data</strong> (upload a CSV/TXT file).
              </p>
